snippet.textDisplay:
Coke Studio Pakistan, can play around with all sorts of toys and enhancement elements, which could be understood as moving with the times or catering to the constant shifts in the musical paradigm, but..... when "RUH" is the constant denominator and it is never compromised; Nothing is Lost in Translation! 
CSP never fails to deliver! CSP Keeps it Real!! CSP elevates the listener to another dimension! 
Other initiatives of a similar sort can try, but they will always lack the Key Concept "RUH"and that cannot be imitated. 
Either you Have it or you Don't!!
